metadata.description:
Back once again with a Mija classic. This time we got "Give 'Em What They Want" 

This song is based off one of my life philosophies, you gotta give the people what they WANT. Then you give them what they NEED. And then give them what they want again :')

20 will be available for free for collectors in my Telegram chat

join us:
https://guild.xyz/mija-collectors

lyrics.text:
Give em what they want
Give em what they need

Never keep a man cause it burns me out
So I fool around and I shake 'em down
And I spin it back around
Back to the 1
Where we started from
And you're having fun??

metadata.name: Give 'Em What They Want #1
metadata.title: Give 'Em What They Want
